---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-900/10 bg-slate-950 py-14 text-slate-300">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <img src="/assets/logo.jpg" alt="MIEF" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl object-cover ring-1 ring-white/10" />
          <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">MIEF</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400">
          Független szakmai közösség, amely a mesterséges intelligencia jogi, etikai, oktatási és társadalmi kérdéseit vizsgálja.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Navigáció</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/#miert" class="hover:text-white">Küldetés</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#kinek" class="hover:text-white">Kinek szól?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#fokusz" class="hover:text-white">Fókuszterületek</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#kapcsolat" class="hover:text-white">Kapcsolat</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tudastar" class="hover:text-white">Tudástár</a></li>
          <li><a href="/english" class="hover:text-white">English Summary</a></li>
          <li><a href="/unsubscribe" class="hover:text-white text-xs text-slate-500">Leiratkozás</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Kapcsolat</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:info@mief.hu" class="hover:text-white flex items-center gap-2 transition">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
              info@mief.hu
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/113130027" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="hover:text-white flex items-center gap-2 transition">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
              LinkedIn oldal
            </a>
          </li>
          <li><span class="text-xs text-slate-500">mief.hu</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} MI Etika Fórum. Minden jog fenntartva.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
